cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper is about scene text recognition, which is a computer vision task, hence cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which falls under cs.CL, cs.LG, and cs.AI. Finally, the paper uses synthetic training data, which could fall under cs.IR (information retrieval) as well.
